Maze Runner

Objective: Get through the maze

Controls: WASD

Designs Goals:
    1. First pass
        i. Basic game loop
            > Loop progressing whenver player makes a valid move
        ii. User input
            > Take from keyboard
            > Reject if going into wall
        iii. Maze tiles
            > Empty spaces
                > Start
                > Finish
            > Walls
    2. Second pass
        i. Randomly generated mazes
            > Different options for maze size and complexity
        ii. Leaderboard
        iii. AI chasing player
        iv. New tiles
            > Opens new passages
